org.anhcraft.spaciouslib.placeholder

Class Placeholder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.anhcraft.spaciouslib.placeholder.Placeholder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CachedPlaceholder

    public abstract class Placeholder
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a placeholder implementation.
    Warning: If you replace the placeholder, you will have the newest data so there is a problem with performance.
    Recommend: Uses FixedPlaceholder or CachedPlaceholder instead.
